  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                               <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018130/extras/7b2f7beeb26c5c92cd0ca09e67ee0ca0.avif?t=1734857730\" width=256 height=128 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Penguin Village is in peril! Everyone has been captured and turned into mindless serfs by the aliens from the sky. Narrowly escaped, you were rescued by the resistance and have trained night and day for this moment. Battle through Penguin's Road in this comical military action shooter and save your hometown.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                                               <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018130/extras/7b2f7beeb26c5c92cd0ca09e67ee0ca0.avif?t=1734857730\" width=256 height=128 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Penguin Village is in peril! Everyone has been captured and turned into mindless serfs by the aliens from the sky. Narrowly escaped, you were rescued by the resistance and have trained night and day for this moment. Battle through Penguin's Road in this comical military action shooter and save your hometown.</p>",
